Installing Git
check if git is installed
git --version

set username for git
git config --global user.name "<Your Name>"
git config --global user.email "<Your Email>"

Creating Repository
mkdir hello-world
cd hello-world
ls
git initcd
git status

Committing to Repo
git status
git add <file-name>
git commit -m "commit message"
git diff

Add username to git
git config --global user.username siftnoorsingh

